data.description: Welcome to this charming home in a NO HOA community! Impeccably maintained and move-in ready, this residence offers the allure of new construction coupled with the advantage of extra space. NEWER WATER HEATER, NEW TOILET! The large front and level backyard, complete with seclusion, provide a perfect setting for outdoor enjoyment. Experience the freedom of a community without homeowners association restrictions, ensuring a lifestyle tailored to your preferences. Don't miss the opportunity to make this well-kept property your new home!
